Description:
    Creates a new AngularJS route
    Docs: https://docs.angularjs.org/api/ngRoute

Example:
    yo angularfire:route thing [--coffee] [--uri=path_to/thing] [--auth-required]

    This will create:
        app/scripts/controllers/thing.js
        app/views/thing.html
    And add routing to:
        app.js
